title: For Sale:  Glock IWB leather holster
postcontent:
Brand new. Right hand. Fits Glock 17 / 19 / 22 / 23 / 24 / 26 / 27 / 31 / 32 / 33 / 34 / 35 / 37 / 38 / 39

For the closest in concealment, the Inside-The-Waistband (IWB) leather holster gives you the deep concealment of inside the pants with a high inner body to protect your shirt or skin from the sharp edges and also to keep the finish of your pistol protected from moisture. Molded on the inside for extra retention, the top of the holster is also reinforced to allow one handed re-holstering. Inside the waistband (IWB) holsters provide the most comfortable and effective concealed carry method for most people. All parts of the holster and pistol that ride below the top of the pants (or skirt) are hidden, making it less likely that the covering garment will be pulled up and expose the holster. The shirt guard is to keep leather between the slide and your body, and to increase comfort and prevent your shirt from blocking the gun holster. The pants and belt hold the pistol close to the body for a flatter profile. This holster is made to fit belts up to 2" wide and attaches by a metal spring clip.

Paypal accepted for payment. 
Free priority mail shipping anywhere in the Continental US. No APO

title: For Sale:  STAG ARMS 3G
postcontent:
Boasting an 18” stainless steel fluted heavy barrel with a rifle length gas system and the new Stag Arms 3G compensator; recoil impulse is greatly reduced allowing for fast follow up shots. Aiding in accuracy is the Samson Evolution hand guard, which is free floating and modular, allowing the attachment of rail sections or sling mounts along the hand guard. This also grants the shooter the ability to mount accessories as needed but not be burdened with a full quad rail. The trigger is a Geissele Super 3-Gun trigger, which was specifically developed for 3-Gun competitions, as the name implies. It possesses a great reputation for durability and has what Geissele calls a hybrid pull. This hybrid pull is a unique combination of a single and two-stage that allows for both quick close range shots and more deliberate long range shots. The buttstock and pistol grip are from Magpul featuring MOE pistol grip that provides a solid and secure grip whith integral emergency field kit. The rifle comes with thel Dueck Defense Rapid Transition Sights (RTS) which are offset iron sights that are used for close in shots.

Comes with the original carry case and NRA waterproof rifle case with foam inserts. Single attach sling. Grip field service kit. Several pre-ban high cap mags and ammunition and a couple of 10rd Stag Mags. This is a great three gun rifle.

The has had only 200 rounds through it.  Relocation forces sales.

title: For Sale:  F.I.E SuperTitan  .380 Auto -- Great condition
postcontent:
Beretta-style autoloader with full-wood grip, two safeties, good trigger action and never a failed cycle.

Made in Italy and distributed by F.I.E. Florida.  I've had this for 15 years in the same night table.  Maybe 150 rounds shot at ranges.  I buffed grips for better grip (less urethane).

Great concealed-carry instrument.  The two safeties make it a secure carry with flexibility in how you park it.

Light weight relative to, say, 9mm, but that makes it compact and accommodating for CC or packing.

Will take offers starting at listed price.  No trades, please, and if you're local or can meet nearby, that will make the deal.
